Class PostGISRasterProvider

    Histogramable, DataStoreProvider, CoverageStoreProvider, RasterProvider, RemoteRasterProvider, Disposable, DynObject

    public class PostGISRasterProvider
extends GdalProvider
implements RemoteRasterProvider
    This class represents the data access just for PostGIS raster databases.

      • loadBuffer

        public void loadBuffer(SpiRasterQuery q)
                throws ProcessInterruptedException,
                       RasterDriverException
        Description copied from class: AbstractRasterProvider
        Load a buffer with the parameters. The buffer should already have been created inside the query structure SpiRasterQuery by the RasterDataStore. The other parameters have been calculated too, all of them adjusted to the raster limits. The provider only have to read the parameters and load the buffer.
        Overrides:
        loadBuffer in class GdalProvider

      • getFileLayer

        public File getFileLayer()
                  throws RasterDriverException
        When the remote layer has fixed size this method downloads the file and return its reference. File layer has in the long side FIXED_SIZE pixels and the bounding box is complete. This file could be useful to build an histogram or calculate statistics. This represents a sample of data.
